reviewText: There is a lot to cover as the description indicates.  I enjoyed the Summit, which took me two weekends to complete.  The manual is decent and the presenters are top notch in the MFT field.  Very helpful in all realms of client interaction, from intake thru treatment to termination.  While pricy, you get a lot for the dollar.  The interaction with the panel is lively and Susan Johnson is definitely  someone I would love to "Tango" with.
